at the bot with rage burning in his spark (talk about
out of character).

Mutate: I WILL DEFEAT YOU! SOMEDAY! BY THE MATRIX YOU
HAVE MY VOW! REMEMBER THAT! SOMEDAY WE WILL MEET
AGAIN!

This had been the most humiliating day of his
unnatural life.

OOC: I'm not exactly thrilled about Nemasis and his
bot kicking my butt either. Am I allowed to post for a
meteorite head straight for him 200 ft. abobe his head
that is big enough to destroy everything within a half
mile radius.
